In yet another attempt to be the hippest White House EVA, Dear President has teamed up with his Number Two for a “Let’s Move!” PSA. But it’s really just an attempt to show off Barack’s athleticism, given questionable videos we’ve seen in the past of him tossing pitches in mom jeans or missing 22 baskets on the b-ball court. For whatever reason, they’ve chosen a remixed former “Monday Night Football” theme to run to, which is one of many reasons this clip looks like the attempt of a first-year video production student.

What would have truly saved this little movie would be if Barack grabbed a cigarette at the end. Or at least an e-cig. I probably would have chuckled.

